                <section class="genesis">
                    <div class="wrap">
                        <div class="wrap-left">
                            <h2>Genesis of Kusama</h2>
                            <p>The interaction between
                                society
                                and
                                technology has evolved into
                                a
                                broken
                                model, where large entities
                                routinely stretch and
                                overstep
                                their
                                authority.
                                <br /><br />
                                Entrusting our information
                                to
                                these
                                organizations presents a
                                critical
                                risk to individuals and
                                society.
                                Kusama was built to spark
                                innovation
                                and disrupt the status quo
                                by
                                putting next-generation
                                tools in
                                the
                                hands of change agents.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="what-is-kusama">
                    <div class="wrap">
                        <div
                            class="wrap-right box-outlines">
                            <h2>What is Kusama?</h2>
                            <p>Kusama is a scalable network
                                of
                                multiple specialized
                                blockchains
                                built using the same tools
                                and
                                nearly the same codebase as
                                Polkadot.
                                <br /><br />
                                The network is a development
                                environment for teams who
                                want
                                to
                                move fast and innovate
                                exclusively
                                on Kusama, or prepare for
                                deployment
                                on Polkadot.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="launch-your-blockchain">
                    <div class="section-hero sticky">
                        <div class="bg-img">
                            <img
                                src="/assets/img/mesh_graph_1.png"
                                alt="Launch your custom blockchain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="h1 large">
                            Launch Your<br />Custom
                            Blockchain
                        </h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="features wrap">
                        <div class="wrap-right">
                            <div class="feature">
                                <h3>Fast Iteration</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Move fast and ship your
                                    product. Kusama’s
                                    risk-taking and nimble
                                    mentality allows
                                    developers
                                    to move swiftly through
                                    the
                                    governance and upgrade
                                    process, enabling rapid
                                    progress and growth.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature">
